sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Customer
  participant API as API Gateway
  participant O as Orders Lambda
  participant D as DynamoDB Orders
  participant E as EventBridge
  participant Q as SQS Fulfillment

  C->>API: POST /orders
  API->>O: invoke
  O->>D: PutItem(orderId, status=CREATED)
  O->>E: PutEvents(OrderCreated)
  E->>Q: enqueue fulfillment task
  O-->>API: 201 Created (orderId)
  API-->>C: orderId + status